<title>AUSTRALIA: RTRS-ADEX sees takeover response in a week.</title>
<headline>RTRS-ADEX sees takeover response in a week.</headline>
<dateline>MELBOURNE 1997-01-03</dateline>
<text>
<p>Australian Diamond Exploration NL (ADEX) said on Friday it expected to make a formal response to the A$1.40 a share takeover offer from Ashton Mining Ltd &quot;probably in another week&quot;.</p>
<p>ADEX chairman Ewen Tyler told Reuters that independent experts from local and U.S. investment banks had been appointed to assess Ashton's offer for the 22.4 percent of ADEX it does not already hold.</p>
<p>Ashton on Friday released its formal Part A statement to the Australian Stock Exchange. ADEX last traded at A$1.36 on Thursday. -- Sydney newsroom 61-2 9373-1800</p>
